---
// About.astro - About section component
export interface Props {
  className?: string;
}

const { className = '' } = Astro.props;
---

<section class={`py-20 bg-gray-900 ${className}`}>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">关于本站</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 bg-slate-800 p-10 rounded-lg">
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <img
          alt="博主头像"
          class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover mx-auto md:mx-0 mb-6"
          src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBcmY4qIJHvmnyMunv5LggxjO9zVEA_0fIYd80-jH4jbILuz8zQJ-cvmeNeqnEqAMC4MU3eSQJ3oTMo4VFGMZHEM9PgQcUPV_8phLMm7bvTX1RDociJsU70Jw1UmdE8-uudmKLBr-QY61aGnEn8yBSjTGONHVA07GQrkBlnzaZKqtgMSJQMDCoaDD7-ndOKk-IrVkCKTNc7d3l3l3s433Bd6a2xpuTZkZkLbaWG1gAL0VLdUNHZex2DQZg6rCzzPhV194YhlXewauj6"
        />
        <div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
            在这个信息爆炸的AI时代，每天都有无数新工具诞生。我创建这个博客，旨在通过亲身实测和深度分析，为你提供最公正、最深入的AI产品评测。
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-semibold">
            我的使命是：在AI的浪潮中，为你过滤噪音，找到真正有价值的工具。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-2xl group">
          <img
            alt="视频介绍缩略图"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCZq0Y9t5w0nD9V9igH5GFKxJA5ysstRpaLz9IPhYGoM6Wqra8O6tzaVCdUOkBoKzaHtqiO8hIWp0-Aol7G6bfIkfR7yEYgbhwdXzUTjq0Ijnm_4Kjo6ge_pLd-C4PRwNMjVcjQAx5Q9xc8dXRnwEV1Ycv4cbOXYum1ggF7I8I1ZEW24KhC5VDa79VQiIsO2VeJwW3rWGKWYyCbhUSod_dzCQ213pMFZM63BGGrPETiPqF8zuLcz42omDknFEWhwH2DluQaQoHOn--V"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-40 flex items-center justify-center">
            <button class="text-white transform transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-125">
              <span class="material-icons text-7xl" style="text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);">play_circle_filled</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-400 mt-4 text-sm">观看视频，了解我们的评测理念</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>